PRONE

Usage: ^gPRONE^N

Going into a prone position allows you to make use of bipod
and tripod attachments on weapons. It also lets you fire heavy
weapons with less than 8 strength and body. 

While prone however you are easier to hit with firearms and much
easier to hit in melee combat. You also do not get a chance to
dodge.

^WSee Also: HEAVY WEAPONS^N
